    <string name="about_description">La Fábrica de Software is an engineering company specialised in the development of integrated information systems with our equipment and machines, for automated management and textile control in hospitals, factories, industrial laundries, dry cleaners, etc.\n\nWe have qualified staff dedicated to research and development of innovative solutions aimed at meeting the specific needs of each of our clients.\n\nWe work every day to obtain all the advantages offered by RFID technology for the identification and management of items in large volumes, providing greater efficacy and efficiency in the processes of hospitals, socio-health centres, laundries and other communities: industry, hotels, gyms, etc.</string>
